Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:18.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的羽翼 已经与你一同消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:27.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔时的记忆 却无法像擦伤一样消去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:37.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你寻回 是我一直所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:45.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你不随时间的浊流 被浪冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:53.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法说出些许回忆 始终无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:01:02.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留下的些许眼泪 却一定无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:08.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的泪滴 也将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:16.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间黑夜被撕裂 光芒飞散于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:24.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洁净如洗的太阳 温柔地照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:30.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱着你一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:41.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描绘出的梦之画卷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:49.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去轻轻触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:55.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伸出的指尖 它淡淡消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:23:03.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 真实的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:13.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧 聆听这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:22.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份满溢的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:32.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定能传达给最重视的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队都到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帐篷中休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣有一事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直说无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军观察到趁着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:02:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辆巨大车辆被搬运到真王军营
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣有听说哈鲁弥亚陛下被袭击时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兽盘旋上空保护真王的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不知道陛下是不是真能引发奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真王为打击我军气势编造的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兽斗蛇都是不会服从于人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得用锁链和训笛束缚住的动物 人类又何以操控
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当战旗摇起的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便无人再能保护王族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只等陛下的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天一亮 我就必须下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟弥亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达弥亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣没能除掉那颗废棋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻一无是处的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你失望之极
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻从我眼前消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他身受重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快能追到 这次绝不会失手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会回来的 那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将精力都还放在那个阿廖身上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘似乎没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想帮帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:12.55,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)}{\fad(1000,0)}{\blur2}辽扎的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪太大连弓箭都用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武艺一点都没退步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神速的伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凯尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你快逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备森严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且 真王陛下和达弥亚大人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是那群替代了坚盾的假面部下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你要一个人去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我也会陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人只会成为负担
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟会说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是接下来的事情我要自己解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一心想要保护家人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才舍弃了他们加入坚盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说哈鲁弥亚陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了一己私欲而杀害伯母的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有资格统治这个国家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那个对我说 该用手去捕捉幸福的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是打算去白白送死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧 帮不上忙只好撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿你寻找到新生之光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊亚尔…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是艾琳背叛了身边的教导师们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么还救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把手伸出来给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我的伤和它们没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:21.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时奇里库给艾琳的是糖果 形状和他使用的暗箭一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 鲁甘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我交付给你保护城堡的斗蛇部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家大事 岂能安守城中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢用大公赐予的斗蛇军力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去胁迫真王服从于你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是造反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有打算让瑟弥亚陛下服从
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我还真想亲眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁甘 你就好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥改变这世界的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重塑亚曼·哈萨鲁未完成的伟业身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运…只掌握在神的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在我这衰老的父亲面前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看到这变革的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家迎来新时代的光芒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当太阳升过地平线之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇里库老师 你还不可以起身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁太阳升起之前…快逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起…好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道前面是光明还黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…会到最后都坚守和比兰一起的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰…就是光明的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是在祈愿光明的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇里库老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇里库老师 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 要活下去 要幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了和泰尔同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还活着的话应该和你同岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也…要幸福地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一决胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心…求死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真令人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是达弥亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两颗废棋同时出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那个女孩身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…不快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能挽救的生命更加不可以放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止血的话 我自己可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要潜入达弥亚身边的话 请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 艾琳就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 还没到你上场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇还在很远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听一听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心声…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明在即
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到光芒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好哭泣的 瑟弥亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他们汇集了多少斗蛇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不曾知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来世界竟是如此宽广 美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的太古时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自亚芬诺亚山脉另一边的真王之祖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降临在塔海亚泽之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王祖如果在这尸横遍地的原野上前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其之上就有王兽展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王祖如果渡河
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇就会垂首 为其铺就道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有光辉的头发和金色的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高大魁梧的王祖杰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛让人们瞻仰着圣洁的神姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比兰 天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:02.89,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:07.44,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾说过不希望王兽成为战场上的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.36,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎来日出的塔海亚泽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:13.71,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇的军队开始向真王发起进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:16.18,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我所能做的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.39,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现你的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:20.63,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓死奋战到底
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.05,0:24:23.47,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽之奏者 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.78,0:24:24.59,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:30.34,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,255)}决战


